    "notes": "Issued in a single pocket sleeve with a soft sheen finish. Printed inner sleeves of thin card, top opening.\nThe lustrous gold vinyl is translucent and has a marbled appearance when held up to light.\nCopies may come with a hype sticker and/or merchant retailing stickers depending on territory.\nBarcode may be in the form of a sticker applied directly to the sleeve, within the shrink-wrap.\n\nSticker on shrink-wrap says \"LIMITED EDITION GOLD VINYL\" (The Target exclusive U.S. release's hype sticker says \"limited edition 2LP gold vinyl\")\n\nThis compilation ℗ & © 1992 Polar Music International AB\nMade in the EU. ",
